Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  書不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒找到嗎  那本「夕暮已成骸」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是暑假的時候帶回老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那來幫忙弄海報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  要萌的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微出去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.45,0:00:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐  記住書名了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千反田同學  摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理大賽上午十一點半開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福  抱歉  我不得不留在漫畫研究社畫海報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  把摩耶花的出場順序放在最後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs16}野火\N11：30先鋒\N11：50中堅\N12：10大將\N每人至少一道菜\N出聲搭話是違規的！\N允許在學校內補給食材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16}體育館舞台\N10：00合唱\N13：30銅管樂隊演奏\N15：30交際舞\N第三天\N9：30話劇\N13：30銅管樂隊演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在十二點十分前趕來就行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  我會想辦法趕來的  待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我也得去總務委員會露個臉  先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是樂在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我把那個箱子搬到體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\bord0\shad0\c000000\fs20\frz247.519\pos(110,138)}客人專用鞋套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  學長不去四處逛逛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟有不少雜務要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是粗略地逛過一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼有趣的事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了  聽說圍棋社出現怪盜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說犯人偷走了棋子  還留下了犯罪聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  在圍棋社啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  不過我估計那只是社員的自導自演而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我聽岡野說  合唱團似乎也發生了類似的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像是保溫箱裡的一瓶飲料不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個也留下犯罪聲明了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎留下了奇怪的紙條
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下變得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  福部  笑嘻嘻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一定會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\bord0\shad0\c000000\fs20\pos(227,135)}萬人的死角  上映中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正小标宋_GBK\shad0\bord0\c000000\frz270\pos(288,170)}\h\h２-Ｆ 自主拍攝\N\N\N\N\N「萬人的死角」手冊50日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您願意接受我的請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等賣出去後再道謝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  社刊多少錢一本  一共有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一本200日元  印了…200本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為一些差錯而印多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我們想盡可能多賣出去一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降價到每本150日元  給我20本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們的手冊一起捆綁銷售賣200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是讓你給我樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  我沒有帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後記得帶上現貨去拜託別人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改善一下求人方式  結果就會很不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入須學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入須學姐很擅長求人辦事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請教教我求人辦事的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管拜託什麼事情  都要誘導對方自主地行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘導對方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:06:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了做到這點  必須要讓對方感到精神上的滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方法雖然有很多  但你能用上的方法應該就是「期待」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  讓對方感到「自己被別人所期待」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓對方感到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能辦到這點  之後對方就會很容易為你效力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為我效力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不要將問題展現得太嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要展現得太嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓對方覺得「雖然對自己無關緊要  但對於對方還蠻重要的」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度就剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡可能在沒人的地方  拜託異性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把社刊拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的一席話令我受益匪淺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給糖就搗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,325)}Trick  or  Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}註：萬聖節孩子們扮鬼求糖果時的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給糖就搗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,325)}Trick  or  Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點心製作研究會的上門銷售  來一份餅乾如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一袋100日元喔  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  這是什麼  好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著這個去推銷似乎不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}那麼用兩袋餅乾做交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在購買社刊的話  附贈這把手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為表達南瓜頭的謝意  這個也送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}全麥粉（小麥粉）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}註：全麥粉蛋白質含量低，\N黏度小，用於製作點心和\N油炸食品的麵衣。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小麥粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不給糖就搗蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,325)}Trick  or  Treat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\shad0\c000000\3cffffff\fs18\an9}超級快速！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\shad0\c000000\3cffffff\fs18\an9}海報繪製生存戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\shad0\c000000\3cffffff\fs18\an9}漫畫研究會引以為傲的繪畫達人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\shad0\c000000\3cffffff\fs18\an9}「魔法少女」VS「美洲獅」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}註：摩耶花\N裝扮的角色是\N《甜蜜小天使》\N裡的加賀美厚子，\N擁有利用鏡子\N變身成任何\N型態的能力。\N河內學姐裝扮的是\N《龍虎之拳》的King，\NKOF對戰角色之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.47,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫研究會引以為傲的繪畫達人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  開工了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\fad(1000,0)}料理研究會  主辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20\fad(1000,0)}WILDFIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎還在忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信摩耶花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們組的須原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他家是經營料亭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}註：料亭是日本特色的高級餐館，價格昂貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就盡量努力吧  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 介紹這次大家矚目的參賽隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一號  好味道隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二號  Fata  Morgana隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}註：Fata  Morgana：源於義大利語，指亞瑟王傳奇中登場的邪惡女巫摩根勒菲，\N而後又意指複雜蜃景（一種不常見且形式複雜的海市蜃樓）。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三號  天文社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是四號  古籍研究社隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽規則  各隊三人一組  每人限時20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經過20分鐘後  就由下一位隊員接手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.35,0:10:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位選手進行料理時  其他選手與其交流將視為犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各位選手注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學打算做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部流  海鮮炒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得比賽裡米飯要用生米現煮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  福部同學就是最後的大將吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我擔當最先登場的先鋒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然做不成海鮮炒飯  什麼時候登場都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊每位隊員都要至少做一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食材從賽場中央籃子裡挑選  先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果食材用完了  允許從校內獲取補給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  先鋒的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(310,325)}On  your  kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wild！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fire
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  野火杯已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(293,325)\fs18}Wild  Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各支隊伍究竟會為我們呈現怎樣的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在令人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古籍研究社隊正在逐一摘除曬魚乾的頭和內臟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好細緻的作法  社長覺得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是很重要的準備工作  副社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fata  Morgana隊  準備好了菲律賓蛤仔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要做蘿蔔醬湯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學  那樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿蔔還沒去皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提建議是犯規的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮  去皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用剝皮器一塊塊地去皮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水已經沸騰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古籍研究社隊  這樣似乎很花費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入了莫比烏斯帶之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs16}莫比烏斯帶：只有一個面和一條邊界的拓撲學結構，用一個紙帶旋轉半圈\N再把兩端黏上即可形成，具有很多奇妙的性質。\N這裡或許來自《涼宮春日的憂鬱》中長門有希的角色歌《Under "Mebius"》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前還看不出各支隊伍做的是什麼料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  古籍研究社隊開始猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燙燙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要做豬肉醬湯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  好味道隊做的是傳統悠久的蕃茄肉醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照這個進度就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各隊的先鋒  時間就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5  4  3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,325)}Change  Element
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊員交換
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}Change  Element：《創聖的大天使》傳送換人時的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  只做出一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了  千反田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是技驚四座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古籍研究社隊的中堅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是精彩的旋切技法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蘿蔔的原本姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  美輪美奐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的話  感覺被汙染的河川也能變得清澈  因為是河嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(541,325)}皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}註：日語中，削蘿蔔皮的「皮」和河流的「河」同音。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  這麼快就做出一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  果然符合千反田同學的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  古籍研究社隊竟然使出合掌淘米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著將僅有六公升的水毫不惋惜地用掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了可口的米飯而做出破釜沉舟的覺悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  快看天文社隊中堅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼  到底是在做什麼料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過激火焰
